components.name: ContactFormComponent
components.templateData:
<form
  class="form"
  [formGroup]="contactForm"
  (submit)="onSubmit()"
  role="form"
  aria-label="Contact Form"
>
  <app-input-field
    type="text"
    name="name"
    formControlName="name"
    id="contact-name"
    autocomplete="name"
    label="Name"
    aria="Write your name."
    errorMessage="Please enter a valid name."
  ></app-input-field>

  <app-input-field
    type="email"
    name="email"
    formControlName="email"
    id="contact-email"
    autocomplete="email"
    label="Email"
    aria="Write your email."
    errorMessage="Please enter a valid email."
  ></app-input-field>

  <app-textarea-field
    name="message"
    formControlName="message"
    id="contact-message"
    label="Write your message..."
    aria="Write your message."
    errorMessage="Please enter a valid message (there is a 300 character limit)."
    cols="20"
    rows="7"
  ></app-textarea-field>

  <button
    class="button-form"
    type="submit"
    role="button"
    [disabled]="contactForm.invalid"
    [attr.aria-disabled]="contactForm.invalid"
  >
    Send
  </button>
</form>
